My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 6 Episode 37

Teams soar to new heights by designing airline food. Their meals will then be served to all passengers onboard a Jetstar 787 flight with the passengers scoring each meal out of 10. The team with the highest score will win People's Choice, while the two weakest dishes as determined by the judges will be sent to the Sudden Death elimination
